#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:1
msgid "Git API"
msgstr "Git API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:3
msgid "Git repository helpers are available under `ptool.git` and `p.git`."
msgstr "Git 仓库辅助能力位于 `ptool.git` 和 `p.git` 下。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:5
msgid ""
"This module is backed by `git2` / `libgit2`, not by invoking the `git` "
"command-line tool."
msgstr "这个模块基于 `git2` / `libgit2`，而不是通过调用 `git` 命令行工具实现。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:8
msgid "ptool.git.open"
msgstr "ptool.git.open"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:10
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:10"
msgid "`Unreleased` - Introduced."
msgstr "`Unreleased` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:12
msgid ""
"`ptool.git.open(path?)` opens a repository directly and returns a `Repo` "
"object."
msgstr "`ptool.git.open(path?)` 直接打开一个仓库，并返回 `Repo` 对象。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:15
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:15"
msgid "Arguments:"
msgstr "参数："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:17
msgid ""
"`path` (string, optional): Repository path. If omitted, the current `ptool` "
"runtime directory is used."
msgstr "`path`（string，可选）：仓库路径。省略时使用当前 `ptool` 运行时目录。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:20
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:20"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:22
msgid ""
"Relative paths are resolved from the current `ptool` runtime directory, so "
"they follow `ptool.cd(...)`."
msgstr "相对路径会从当前 `ptool` 运行时目录解析，因此会跟随 `ptool.cd(...)`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:24
msgid ""
"This does not search parent directories. Use `ptool.git.discover(...)` when "
"you want repository discovery behavior."
msgstr "这个 API 不会向父目录继续搜索仓库。如果你需要仓库发现行为，请使用 "
"`ptool.git.discover(...)`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:27
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:27"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:34
msgid "ptool.git.discover"
msgstr "ptool.git.discover"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:36
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:36"
msgid "`Unreleased` - Introduced."
msgstr "`Unreleased` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:38
msgid ""
"`ptool.git.discover(path?)` finds a repository starting from `path` and "
"walking up parent directories, then returns a `Repo` object."
msgstr "`ptool.git.discover(path?)` 从 `path` 开始向上遍历父目录查找仓库，然后返回一"
"个 `Repo` 对象。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:41
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:41"
msgid "Arguments:"
msgstr "参数："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:43
msgid ""
"`path` (string, optional): Starting path. If omitted, the current `ptool` "
"runtime directory is used."
msgstr "`path`（string，可选）：起始路径。省略时使用当前 `ptool` 运行时目录。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:46
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:46"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:48
msgid "Relative paths are resolved from the current `ptool` runtime directory."
msgstr "相对路径会从当前 `ptool` 运行时目录解析。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:49
msgid ""
"This is useful when a script may run from a subdirectory inside a worktree."
msgstr "当脚本可能在 worktree 的某个子目录中运行时，这个 API 很有用。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:51
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:51"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:58
msgid "ptool.git.clone"
msgstr "ptool.git.clone"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:60
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:60"
msgid "`Unreleased` - Introduced."
msgstr "`Unreleased` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:62
msgid ""
"`ptool.git.clone(url, path[, options])` clones a repository and returns a "
"`Repo` object for the cloned repository."
msgstr "`ptool.git.clone(url, path[, options])` 克隆一个仓库，并返回该克隆仓库对应的 "
"`Repo` 对象。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:65
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:65"
msgid "Arguments:"
msgstr "参数："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:67
msgid "`url` (string, required): Remote repository URL."
msgstr "`url`（string，必填）：远端仓库 URL。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:68
msgid "`path` (string, required): Destination path."
msgstr "`path`（string，必填）：目标路径。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:69
msgid "`options` (table, optional): Clone options. Supported fields:"
msgstr "`options`（table，可选）：克隆选项。支持的字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:69
msgid "`branch` (string, optional): Branch name to check out after cloning."
msgstr "`branch`（string，可选）：克隆完成后要检出的分支名。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:69
msgid ""
"`bare` (boolean, optional): Whether to create a bare repository. Defaults to "
"`false`."
msgstr "`bare`（boolean，可选）：是否创建裸仓库。默认值为 `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:69
msgid "`auth` (table, optional): Remote authentication settings."
msgstr "`auth`（table，可选）：远端认证设置。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:75
msgid "`auth` fields:"
msgstr "`auth` 字段："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:77
msgid "`kind` (string, required): Authentication mode. Supported values:"
msgstr "`kind`（string，必填）：认证模式。支持的值："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:77
msgid "`\"default\"`: Use libgit2 default credentials."
msgstr "`\"default\"`: 使用 libgit2 的默认凭据。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:77
msgid "`\"ssh_agent\"`: Authenticate through the local SSH agent."
msgstr "`\"ssh_agent\"`: 通过本地 SSH agent 进行认证。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:77
msgid "`\"userpass\"`: Use a plaintext username and password."
msgstr "`\"userpass\"`: 使用明文用户名和密码。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:81
msgid "`username` (string, optional): Username for `\"ssh_agent\"`."
msgstr "`username`（string，可选）：用于 `\"ssh_agent\"` 的用户名。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:82
msgid "`username` (string, required): Username for `\"userpass\"`."
msgstr "`username`（string，必填）：用于 `\"userpass\"` 的用户名。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:83
msgid "`password` (string, required): Password for `\"userpass\"`."
msgstr "`password`（string，必填）：用于 `\"userpass\"` 的密码。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:85
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:85"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:87
msgid ""
"Relative destination paths are resolved from the current `ptool` runtime "
"directory."
msgstr "相对目标路径会从当前 `ptool` 运行时目录解析。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:89
msgid ""
"Authentication options are also used by `repo:fetch(...)` and `repo:push(...)"
"`."
msgstr "认证选项同样会被 `repo:fetch(...)` 和 `repo:push(...)` 使用。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/git.md:92
